Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini, Mahan di bagian sayap\Nakan mengoper bola ke Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahel akan melindungi\Ndan bertahan dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, setelah Mahan dan yang lain kembali,\Nmari lakukan simulasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus memenangkan kejuaraan kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak bisa membiarkan\NAkademi Decelis terus bersikap arogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, Kapten?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sedang membahas\Nstrategi pertandingan Nightball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu betul-betul mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu apa yang kami katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sederhananya,\Naku hanya perlu mencetak angka, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Khan tampak agak aneh hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia terus melamun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang apa yang bisa terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dari mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anjing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sengaja cari ribut, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ini undangan pesta ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin aku hadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa juga yang mau merayakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kalian bilang ingin datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami hanya bersikap sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik kamu segera istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia terpengaruh gerhana bulan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kita sungguh tidak menduga\Nakan bertemu manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengirimi mereka undangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak punya pilihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha ingin mengundang mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu keinginan Sooha, apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, merayakan ulang tahunku\Ndengan manusia serigala itu menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Sooha menyukai mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena dia benci vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ingatkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan pernah pulih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan diambil hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha juga mengatakan itu\Nkarena tidak tahu kalau kita vampir, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Sooha tahu identitas asli kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia mungkin tidak akan mau\Nmenemui kita lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendapatnya tidak ada hubungannya\Ndengan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku melarang\Nterlalu dekat dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin berteman dengan Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sungguh tidak menduga\Ndia sangat membenci vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tidak akan ada\Nyang menyukai vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sudut pandang manusia,\Nwajar kalau mereka membenci kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlebih, vampir membunuh temannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kita tidak pernah menyakiti manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kita yang tahu itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi manusia, kita tidak berbeda\Ndari vampir lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya karena kita bilang\Nkita pengecualian,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan berarti dia akan percaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita tidak bisa memaksa Sooha\Nmemercayai kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, tidak ada\Nyang mau memercayai kita sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kita tidak punya pilihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus memberi tahu Sooha\Nbahwa Solon adalah vampir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk membersihkan nama kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Solon adalah vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kami juga terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah membuang waktu.\NAyo singkirkan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, kayu bakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunyalakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir penuh kebencian, matilah!\NRasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Solon, kami tidak akan pernah\Nmelupakan pengorbananmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu akan selamanya hidup di hati kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noa, kenapa kamu mengumpulkan kayu bakar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jino juga tidak ragu untuk menyalakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengumpulkan banyak sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah tanggung, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kamu berkorban,\Nmasalahnya akan selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kamu saja yang dikorbankan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti berdebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenai rencana ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mari kita pilih dua kandidat dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kandidat untuk apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar dia tidak mengetahui\Nidentitas asli kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita harus berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan gunakan kekuatan kita juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau identitas asli kita ketahuan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita mungkin tidak bisa tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kita bisa tinggal\Ndi sekolah ini untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski Sooha tahu kita vampir,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia mungkin\Ntidak akan memberi tahu siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}siapa juga yang tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir tak punya perasaan seperti cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir hanyalah monster\Nyang dingin dan kejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia serigala jauh lebih baik\Ndibandingkan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, mereka tak bisa dibandingkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vampir yang terburuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya kamu di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf soal tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sengaja terbawa emosi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu betapa kamu membenci vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar reaksimu begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa memberikan ini padamu tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian bilang ulang tahun kalian\Nsebentar lagi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kamu datang,\Nsemuanya pasti akan senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Datang, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, ulang tahun siapa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang tahu\Nkapan ulang tahun kami sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, di hari ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hari saat kami kabur\Ndari panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kabur dari Panti Asuhan Vamfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita sangat menderita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih percaya manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang mengejar kita, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian kabur dari panti asuhan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gudang ini tidak dipakai.\NKalian bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir,\Naku tidak akan memberi tahu siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung ada yang menolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari istirahat sebelum kita pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahanlah sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian lapar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini makanan sisa, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar vampir muncul di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus segera membunuh mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya kalian di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah kubilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di luar panti asuhan berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kembalilah\Nke Rumah Vamfield bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hanya bisa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saling memercayai satu sama lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katamu temanmu dibunuh vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian dekat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini, aku sangat kuat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, semua orang di sekitarku\Nmengira aku vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku selalu sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku juga melarangku
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menggunakan kekuatan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya Chris yang memahamiku di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi suatu hari...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris masih di dalam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak boleh masuk ke sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan aku!\NChris tidak bisa berjalan dengan baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu,\Nyang kupikirkan hanyalah menyelamatkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada yang melihatmu,\Nmereka akan salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mungkin mengira kamu vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli pendapat orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli apa kata mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, aku akan mengeluarkanmu dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tiba-tiba merasa kemampuanku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin ada untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu percaya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu akan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}datang dan menyelamatkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku tak akan pernah bertemu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}teman lain seperti Chris dalam hidup ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan menyuruhku menggigit lehernya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang,\N"Karena aku percaya kamu bukan vampir."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sendiri tidak memercayai diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin\Naku bisa menyukai vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau mencoba menggigit leherku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.\NApa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya aku tidak menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja kami masih kecil saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang sangat berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kita
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}perlahan tumbuh dewasa, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, itulah yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, gigitlah aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Ini terlalu memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku memercayaimu seperti dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu berani menggigit leherku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kan?\NKamu juga merasa malu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}alasan lain aku ingin bersekolah di sini
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah perpustakaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ada banyak buku lama di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira aku bisa menemukan\Nkelemahan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi beberapa saat lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah vampir muncul di alun-alun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kali pertamaku melihat vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah setakut itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga gemetar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seolah-olah seluruh tubuhku membeku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi karena itu, aku menjadi yakin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa vampir benar-benar monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah membawakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya menantikan kehadiranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mahan, bagaimana di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami masih belum tahu ke mana\Nteman-teman kita yang hilang dibawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sepertinya vampir\Nterlihat di sekitar sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menemukan pembunuh siswi itu,\Nkita menyusup ke Akademi Decelis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi vampir itu tampaknya\Ntak ada hubungannya dengan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak akan mengatakan\Nyang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, yang membunuh teman-teman kita\Nadalah vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi beberapa saat lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita melihat mereka melawan vampir lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya kurasa\Nmereka tak di pihak yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada beberapa manusia serigala\Nyang hilang di kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin vampir ada hubungannya\Ndengan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ketahuan kamu manusia serigala,\Nmereka akan mengincarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati saat berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu akan kembali tepat waktu\Nuntuk Nightball, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Camill, kamu masih bisa main, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, nanti kuhubungi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Khan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Khan kesal karena tak bisa berubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang peduli soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, tidak ada yang lebih cocok\Nmenjadi kapten selain Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua orang memikirkan hal yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu hibrida\Nmanusia serigala dan vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga tidak tahu\Nbagaimana aku lahir di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-temanku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa para manusia serigala itu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan benar-benar datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tidak membalas undangan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mungkin tidak akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita membuat persiapan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seandainya jumlahnya tiba-tiba bertambah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih pandai menggambar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bekerja keras untuk mahakarya ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli menjatuhkan kuenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita masih punya waktu.\NMari kita buat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak baik merayakan ulang tahun\Ntanpa kue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkita harus beli bahan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta tolong ke Jakah saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu?\NBagus, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jakah, bisa tolong pergi belanja sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, serahkan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lah? Gosong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuat kalian menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung ada Jakah di saat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak ada di daftar belanja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heli, kamu lupa menulisnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, apa kita butuh ramen\Nuntuk pesta ulang tahun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah dipikir-pikir...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita butuh ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi lagi, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah hampir waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah menunggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini indah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini di tengah hutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menuju ke sini pasti sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku memang terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menduga\Nada rumah seindah ini jauh di dalam hutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kan?\NAku yang membangunnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami hanya mewarisinya dari seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kami meninggalkan panti asuhan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada seseorang yang selalu membantu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mengurus kami dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah dia meninggal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menyerahkan rumah ini pada kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, biasanya kami tinggal di asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami hanya bisa ke sini di akhir pekan\Natau liburan musim panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamannya juga indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membantu merawatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu juga bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuklah, aku akan mengajakmu berkeliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sooha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei... Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, di Episode 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulan Musim Berburu: Pesta Ulang Tahun.
